@@ -19,8 +19,17 @@ Email verification code remains in the repository for future re-enable, but it i
 ### 1) `GET /csrf-token`
 Returns an anonymous CSRF token and sets `anon_csrf` cookie.
 
+CSRF contract:
+- Send the token returned by this endpoint as `X-CSRF-TOKEN` for anonymous state-changing auth requests.
+- Anonymous state-changing endpoints validate `X-CSRF-TOKEN` against the `anon_csrf` cookie.
+- Authenticated state-changing endpoints validate `X-CSRF-TOKEN` against `csrf_access_token`, except `/refresh`, which validates against `csrf_refresh_token`.
+- Missing CSRF header/cookie pairs return `401` with `detail: "Missing CSRF token"`.
+- Mismatched CSRF header/cookie pairs return `401` with `detail: "CSRF token mismatch"`.
